    "name": "The Little UNI",
    "steam_appid": 3096560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这款游戏是基于韩国Vocaloid“UNI”开发的同人游戏，游戏中的角色和故事与官方设定无关。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096560/extras/3e1a7b4db6d90a5d2fbc9497332a82bd.avif?t=1770449110\" width=600 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的主角小UNI在与“玫瑰”发生冲突后，离开了她曾经生活的星球，踏上了寻找新家园的旅程。离开过去一直居住的星球去寻找新的宜居星球并非易事，但聆听那些生活在风格各异的星球上的人们的故事，与他们度过一段难忘的时光，必定是一种美妙的经历。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096560/extras/24dfadbf2ab60d8e991637af30aa7bd4.avif?t=1770449110\" width=600 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聆听各种角色的故事，并欣赏精美的手绘插图。在不同的星球、人物和故事之间，小UNI将做出怎样的最终选择呢？敬请期待。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096560/extras/06d9009ce8fce6bfb51446a4c35a81ac.avif?t=1770449110\" width=600 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小UNI会回到“玫瑰”所在的星球，还是会找到一个新的星球定居呢？</p>",
